[0.422997, "o", "\r\n\r\n  ╭── L3 REASONING  ·  Neural Subroutine  (BatteryAgent)\r\n  │\r\n  │  Agent    GridBattery-E  (battery)\r\n  │  Charge   25.0 / 50.0 MWh  (50%)\r\n  │  Memory   0 experiences stored\r\n  │  Max Chg  25.0 MW  ·  RTE  90%\r\n  │\r\n  │  LLM Input Context  (built dynamically from environment + memory):\r\n  │    Market Price    $ 50.00 / MWh\r\n  │    Grid Demand          372.8 MWh\r\n  │    Grid Frequency  50.000 Hz\r\n  │    Price Trend     stable\r\n  │\r\n  │  LLM Output  (decoded strategy JSON):\r\n  │    ├─ Bid Price     $  1.00\r\n  │    ├─ Action        sell\r\n  │    ├─ Reasoning     Default strategy, following market\r\n  │    ├─ Confidence    71%\r\n  │    └─ Latency       0.1 ms\r\n  │\r\n  │  ├─ Safety Guardrail  Hold  (price within neutral band)\r\n\r\n  ╭── SYMBOLIC ENGINE  ·  DoubleSidedAuction  (Uniform Price)\r\n  │\r\n  │  Market Clearing Price  $38.86 / MWh\r\n  │  Total Supply Traded      372.81 MWh\r\n  │  Demand Met               372.81 MWh\r\n  │  Supply-Demand Δ           -0.00 MWh\r\n  │\r\n  │  ╭─ Matched Orders  ───────────────────────────────────────╮\r\n  │  │ MetroCity           ←  SolarFarm-A           5.02 MW  @ $32.50   │\r\n  │  │ MetroCity           ←  WindFarm-B            0.88 MW  @ $32.50   │\r\n  │  │ MetroCity           ←  NuclearPlant-D      285.00 MW  @ $35.00   │\r\n  │  │ MetroCity           ←  CoalPlant-C          81.91 MW  @ $52.75   │\r\n  │  ╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\r\n  │\r\n  │  Clearing Math:  clearing_price = weighted_avg(matched_prices)\r\n  │                 buyer_surplus  = Σ qty × (wtp − clearing_price)\r\n  │                 seller_surplus  = Σ qty × (clearing_price − marginal_cost)\r\n\r\n  ╭── L6 GOVERNANCE  ·  RegulatoryAgent Oversight\r\n  │\r\n  │  ├── Frequency Guard\r\n  │  │     Threshold  49.0 – 51.0 Hz\r\n  │  │     Actual     50.000 Hz\r\n  │  │     Status     ✅  PASS\r\n  │\r\n  │  ├── Carbon Cap  50000.0 kg\r\n  │  │     CoalPlant-C     