[0.440757, "o", "     │       ▼\r\n  │       │  sim._run_step() guardrails + override\r\n  └───────┘       │\r\n                    ▼\r\n  ┌───────┐\r\n  │SYMBOLIC│  DoubleSidedAuction.clear_market()\r\n  │ENGINE │       │\r\n  │       │       ▼\r\n  │       │  Sort buys  ↓price, sells ↑price\r\n  │       │  Match at uniform clearing price\r\n  │       │  Compute surplus, carbon cost\r\n  └───────┘       │\r\n                    ▼\r\n  ┌───────┐\r\n  │L6     │  RegulatoryAgent\r\n  │GOVERN-│       │\r\n  │ANCE   │       ▼\r\n  │       │  check_frequency(49.0–51.0 Hz)\r\n  │       │  check_carbon(cap threshold)\r\n  │       │  check_market_fairness()\r\n  │       │       │\r\n  │       │       ▼\r\n  │       │  Violations → GridOrchestrator\r\n  │       │  Orchestrator.stabilize()\r\n  │       │       │\r\n  │       │       ▼\r\n  │       │  Frequency correction → next step\r\n  └───────┘\r\n\r\n  Result Summary:\r\n    Steps executed    : 3\r\n    Final frequency   :  50.000 Hz\r\n    Total violations  :  0\r\n    Agent balances    :\r\n      SolarFarm-A           $  742.95\r\n      WindFarm-B            $ 2657.20\r\n      CoalPlant-C           $ 5842.41\r\n      NuclearPlant-D        $29925.00\r\n      GridBattery-E         $    0.00\r\n      MetroCity             $-42881.34\r\n    Price history     :  ['$38.9', '$39.3', '$34.5']\r\n"]
